Custom Crating for Fragile, High‑Value & Specialized Goods

Certain cargo categories require extra care—and that extra care starts with the crate.

Artwork & Antique Protection

Art and antiques demand sensitive packing, structural support, and environmental protection. Our custom crating integrates cushioned interior supports and protective barriers designed to reduce shock and moisture infiltration.

Medical & Scientific Equipment Crating

Precision instruments and healthcare technology require stable, vibration‑resistant crating that protects calibration and delivers safe transit. Our crates are engineered with internal bracing to isolate sensitive gear.

Industrial Machines & Heavy Goods

Large, heavy, or asymmetrical items pose a different challenge—one solved by reinforced wood framing, forklift‐ready bases, and tailored handling access points.

